Name: Battleship Bomber VI
Desc:
Summons a battleship with Nautilus sailors. The battleship's cannon attack does not cause you to take damage even when attacking enemies in the Damage Reflection Status.
Bombs the location by placing a Sign of Bombard in a certain area.
Required Skill: Battleship Bomber Lv. 15 or higher and Ahoy Mateys Lv. 15 or higher
